OL,3,CLibraries light-up in solidarity to
OL,4,Cmark re-opening of arson-hit library
OL,6,FITV News' Tim Scott spoke to
OL,7,Ffundraisers in Liverpool about the
OL,8,Freopening of Spellow Community Hub and
OL,9,FLibrary
OL,11,FLibraries all over the UK were lit up
