OL,3,CLibraries light-up in solidarity to
OL,4,Cmark re-opening of arson-hit library
OL,6,FSpellow Community Hub and Library in
OL,7,FWalton will be officially re-opened in
OL,8,Fspecial ceremony on Thursday, 12
OL,9,FDecember but, the night before,
OL,10,Flibraries united in a nationwide
OL,11,Fsymbolic act called 'Share The Light.'
OL,13,FThe British Library in London is among
OL,14,Fmore than 135 libraries around the
OL,15,Fcountry taking part as well as
OL,16,Flibraries across the North West of
OL,17,FEngland.
