OL,3,CLibraries light-up in solidarity to
OL,4,Cmark re-opening of arson-hit library
OL,6,FThe library was partly destroyed by
OL,7,Frioters on Saturday, 3 August,
OL,8,Ffollowing the murder of schoolgirls
OL,9,FBebe King, Alice Dasilva Aguiar and
OL,10,FElsie Dot Stancombe in Southport.
OL,12,FWhen firefighters arrived at the site
OL,13,Fon County Road, the rioters attempted
OL,14,Fto stop them from getting to the fire
OL,15,Fto put it out.
OL,17,FThe library, which was opened in 2023
OL,18,Fto provide support for one of the most
OL,19,Fdeprived communities in the country,
OL,20,Fsuffered severe damage to the ground
OL,21,Ffloor.
