OL,3,CLibraries light-up in solidarity to
OL,4,Cmark re-opening of arson-hit library
OL,6,FThe arson attack prompted a huge
OL,7,Foutcry and a nationwide response, with
OL,8,Fbook donations from Her Majesty the
OL,9,FQueen and a host of famous authors.
OL,11,FSpecial recognition was given to Alex
OL,12,FMcCormick from Netherton who launched
OL,13,Fa GoFundMe page to repair and restock
OL,14,Fthe library.
OL,16,FAlex said she had felt angry and upset
OL,17,Fat the damage and was aiming to raise
OL,18,F#500 but to her her amazement the fund
OL,19,Freached #250,000.
