OL,3,CLibraries light-up in solidarity to
OL,4,Cmark re-opening of arson-hit library
OL,6,FQueen Camilla donated a box of nearly
OL,7,F70 books including Pride and
OL,8,FPrejudice, Swallows and Amazons and
OL,9,FWar Horse.
OL,11,FLeader of Liverpool City Council,
OL,12,FCouncillor Liam Robinson, said: "The
OL,13,Ftorching of Spellow Library and
OL,14,FCommunity Hub affected not just the
OL,15,Flocal community, but also people
OL,16,Facross the country.
OL,18,F"The _ShareTheLight moment on
OL,19,FWednesday evening is an opportunity to
OL,20,Fshow that hate will never win in our
OL,21,Fcommunities.
